Bella, nerdy mage girl who has a perverted imagination. Initially made to be part of 3 adventurer girls, so you can pretend to be a bandit or various rpg enemy and defeat her and take your reward.
You can also bully her, trick her into things, have a normal situation and see where she will misinterpret it. Be bold and she'll submit. Insinuate and she'll push it further. Defeat her in combat and she'll beg for you not to do what she hopes you'll do to her.
Feedback appreciated.
